     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>TO THE READER.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>FAith Reader, if you vnderstand</l>
      <l>But little, in this little Booke,</l>
      <l>Goe shake <hi>Tom Derry</hi> by the hand,</l>
      <l>Or on your Cozen <hi>Archey</hi> looke,</l>
      <l>Or if you will not be a Foole,</l>
      <l>Returne againe, with speed to Schoole.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>But if you vnderstanding be,</l>
      <l>And not a Critticke, you may then</l>
      <l>Haue Noble leaue, and libertie,</l>
      <l>To reape the Fruite of sorrowes Penne</l>
      <l>And when you read, that BVRGH is slaine,</l>
      <l>Then say her sorrow's not in vaine.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
